        "This step recovers missing Liabilities values wherever both Assets and\n",
        "StockholdersEquity are available, by computing Liabilities as Assets minus\n",
        "StockholdersEquity. This recovery is applied only where the direct\n",
        "Liabilities value is missing, so directly reported values are never\n",
        "overwritten."
